subject: Football (College)
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Josh Hicks ran for 202 yards and a touchdown, and Rutgers beat North Carolina, 40-21, in the inaugural Quick Lane Bowl at Ford Field in Detroit.
